		&nbsp;<a href="pop_profile.asp?mode=display&amp;id=3583"><img src="icon_profile.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Show Profile" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>
        
			&nbsp;<a href="JavaScript:openWindow('pop_mail.asp?id=3583')"><img src="icon_email.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Email Poster" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=34289&amp;TOPIC_ID=4386&amp;FORUM_ID=2&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=General+Discussions&amp;Topic_Title=AOE+groups+wtf%3F&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         bout 3 weeks befor ethe acryia nerf i spent alot of time AEing in acrylia(bout 8 points or so)</P><P>at 1st i was hesitant since i dont like people letting me group as a favor, but once i got the hang of it, i have to say, necros are the BEST 6th person in an AE group(arguably bards are better), the other 5 being 2 epic wizzys, 2 chanters, and 1 cleric</P><P>with 2 DAs you can pull like a motherfucker, even in acrylia where the aggro/assist range on mobs is the size of a pea i would pull trains that would give you shit stains</P><P>that + vex + zveefers + mindwrack = ALOT of mana/hp to group(and unlike bard/cleric) we can heal pullers even if theyre across the zone(zveefers)</P><P>where bards own us is that they have an AE dot, critting word of whateverthe hell is cool but its shit for damage(anyone else wish they had that poison AE spell from CT?)</P><P>i tried AEing in the hole, /shrug looks like more work than its worth<BR>the deep, lure root proc, no thanks<BR>HS, went once, but unless north/west/basement arent camped, your gonna get shitty xp(and need a rog to pic, and rogs are useless in AE)</P><P>all in all, AE is a diff type of play, and real enjoyable to do (if you get the opportunity)<BR>even if its shitty xp or whatever, nice to get a view of that side of the street</P><P><BR>Kriista Silence<BR>Warlock of Veeshan</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=103458" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=103458</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
